highlights.text: Jin has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Don’t Say You Love Me” is the highest at #1.
“你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 457 weeks straight.
“WHERE IS MY HUSBAND!” by RAYE is the highest new entry on Top Songs Singapore at #118.
“Romantic Homicide” by d4vd is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 131 spots at #38.
